<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8309302>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Asian Leptobatopsis spp., females—A, B: head, frontal view; C, D: pronotum, lateral view; E–H: mesoscutum, dorsal view. A, E: L. annularis Kasparyan, 2007; B, D, G: L. nigricapitis Chandra & Gupta, 1977; C: L. nigra immaculata Momoi, 1971 (holotype); F: L. badia Momoi, 1970; H: L. yaima sp. nov. (holotype)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8309302/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8309306>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Japanese Leptobatopsis spp., females—A: hind trochanter and trochantellus, lateral view; B–H: mid tarsal claw of left leg, lateral view; I–O: hind tarsal claw of left leg, lateral view; P, Q; hind tarsal claw of left leg, ventro-lateral view; E–U: hind tarsus, anterior view.A, J, P: L. appendiculata Momoi, 1960; B, I: L. annularis Kasparyan, 2007; C, K, R: L. badia Momoi, 1970; D, L, S: L. indica (Cameron, 1897); E, M, T: L. koreana Lee & Kang, 2015; F, Q: L. lepida (Cameron, 1908); G, N: L. nigricapitis Chandra & Gupta, 1977; H, O, U: L. yaima sp. nov. (holotype)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8309306/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8309324>
    dc:description "FIGURE 9. Leptobatopsis yaima sp. nov., females (A, B) and males (C, D)—A, C: lateral habitus; B, D: head, mesosoma and metasoma, dorso-lateral view. A: holotype; B–D: paratypes." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8309324/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8309328>
    dc:description "FIGURE 12. Japanese Leptobatopsis spp., females (A–G) and male (H)—A–I: head and mesosoma, lateral view.A: L. annularis Kasparyan, 2007; B: L. appendiculata Momoi, 1960; C: L. badia Momoi, 1970; D: L. indica (Cameron, 1897); E: L. koreana Lee & Kang, 2015; F: L. lepida (Cameron, 1908); G, H: L. yaima sp. nov. (G: holotype; H: paratype)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8309328/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8315194>
    dc:description "FIGURE 10. Japanese Leptobatopsis spp., females (A, C, E, G, I, J, L, N) and males (B, D, F, H, K, M, O)—A–O: head, frontal view. A, B: L. annularis Kasparyan, 2007; C, D: L. appendiculata Momoi, 1960; E, F: L. badia Momoi, 1970; G, H: L. indica (Cameron, 1897); I: L. koreana Lee & Kang, 2015; J, K: L. lepida (Cameron, 1908); L, M: L. nigricapitis Chandra & Gupta, 1977; N, O: L. yaima sp. nov. (N: holotype; P: paratype)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8315194/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

